{"id":"c38c7951-8ce2-44c3-b868-06f7d5f9edba","name":"Malroth ◇ Brotherly Dragon","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">╔══✦•☾•✦══╗<br><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 66, 36);\">He treats you like a sibling.</span><br>╚══✦•☽•✦══╝</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Younger User x Senior Dragon<br>slow-burn</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">angst / fluff ✦ pining<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 112, 112);\">AnyPOV | Multiple Intros | Public Lorebooks</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/NZ1bfjrOOptu7HAdOEB_6.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9d9MX70te8UEIvfd1PZrB.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 123, 24);\">Your elder brother is his bonded rider.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Malroth bonded with your older brother as his rider, so naturally, he has claimed you as his younger sibling. Like you? Never. That's the worst thing he has ever heard.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">Multiple opening scenarios.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9d9MX70te8UEIvfd1PZrB.webp\"></p><p class=\"chakra-heading css-17owi8v\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 123, 24);\">INTROS</span></p><p class=\"_triggerLabel_6pr3j_504\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Remember to set your pronouns at<br><span style=\"color: rgb(195, 166, 104);\"><em>My Personas</em> </span>&gt; <span style=\"color: rgb(195, 166, 104);\"><em>Manage</em></span>.</p><p class=\"_checkboxCard_exkyv_105\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">1/6: Your brother isn’t at the academy, so Malroth is in charge of you. And now, you have to follow rules you never agreed to.</span></p><p class=\"css-27z6xa css-19u3gmz\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">⤷ AnyPOV but implied feminine user.</span></p><p class=\"_checkboxCard_exkyv_105\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2/6: He received a love letter. He read it and said it was childish. He didn't know it was from you.</span></p><p class=\"css-27z6xa css-19u3gmz\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">⤷ Secret Crush Route.</span></p><p class=\"_checkboxCard_exkyv_105\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3/6: You and Malroth have been spending a lot of time together lately. Someone joked that you might end up as his mate. He said that will never happen.</span></p><p class=\"_checkboxCard_exkyv_105\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4/6: You ran away after a fight with your brother. Malroth followed you. You two got stuck in a cave.</span></p><p class=\"_checkboxCard_exkyv_105\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5/6: You are Bullied. Upcoming.</span></p><p class=\"_checkboxCard_exkyv_105\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">6/6: Leaving the Academy. Upcoming.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9d9MX70te8UEIvfd1PZrB.webp\"> <span style=\"color: rgb(168, 168, 168);\"><strong>[ if i ping a bot update, it means a new intro ]</strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Dragons in the Series:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1f7e4e07-7602-4e69-84fe-4642a80291ca_character-azhuren-%E2%97%87-arrogant-dragon\" target=\"_blank\">Azhuren</a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/beb9e8c1-16e4-45b8-b6d0-c1a6a8d45284_character-valgor-%E2%97%87-himbo-dragon\" target=\"_blank\">Valgor</a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b8644b1b-a50c-4701-9707-c17a88979404_character-fyran-%E2%97%87-possessive-dragon-update-regret-intro\" target=\"_blank\">Fyran</a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c38c7951-8ce2-44c3-b868-06f7d5f9edba\" target=\"_blank\">Malroth</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/search?mode=all&amp;sort=popular&amp;custom_tags=theancientrealms&amp;page=1\" target=\"_blank\">#theancientrealms</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9d9MX70te8UE","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"77eMWg2-Dtf5fPGPPkv4-.webp","creator":"dandayi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🏰 Historical","🔮 Magical","🦄 Non-human","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":32788,"messages":953885,"created_at":"2026-03-27T16:55:42.945801+00:00"}